title: Sridevi’s Younger Daughter Khushi Kapoor Looks Ethereal In This Photo
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 10 . 2017 Jhanvi & Khushi Kapoor (Source: Instagram | @Sridevi.Kapoor) 
S ridevi’ s daughters Jhanvi Kapoor and Khushi Kapoor are quite the fashionistas . These young girls always manage to pleasantly surprise us with their fashion choices and people across the country even call them the Indian Kendall+Kylie Jenner ! Cool, eh? Check out this photo I found on the Internet of Khushi Kapoor from a wedding. She looks absolutely ethereal. A post shared by @jhanvikapoor on Mar 8, 2017 at 9:12pm PST 
How so gorgeous?! Uff. Here’s another photo in case you’d missed it. A post shared by @jhanvikapoor on Mar 4, 2017 at 8:52pm PST 2
